CBRE is delighted to present, 46 Bonview Circuit, Truganina, for sale. 

Situated at the intersection of Leakes and Forsyth Road, Truganina, 'The Crossing' is centrally placed within one of Australia's fastest growing residential and employment catchments.

This block, located at 46 Bonview Circuit, offers great proximity to major road, rail and port infrastructure. With designated retail, commercial and industrial precincts, 'The Crossing' is set to accommodate a vast cross-section of small, medium and large businesses along with a diverse customer base.

'The Crossing' provides pre-lease, land purchase and turn key options allowing your business to secure its position within the west's premier mixed use business park.

Property highlights include:
+ Land area: 1,350sqm*
+ Corner site
+ 40 metre* street frontage on southern boundary
+ 18 metre* street frontage on western boundary
+ 250 metres* to Leakes Road
+ Exceptionally landscaped streetscapes and entrance statements within the estate
+ Separate access/egress points providing unrivaled accessibility to the surrounding areas and beyond
+ Multiple signalised intersections accessing the site
+ Connections through to parklands and external amenity to the west and south
+ Proposed estate cafe offering city style food and drink
+ Retail and services precinct located along Leakes Road
+ Architecturally designed buildings

For further information or to arrange an on-site inspection, please contact the CBRE team.

*approximate

 + Benefiting from major infrastructure works including the proposed Truganina Train Station and the West Gate Tunnel by 2022

 + Truganina has experienced a tremendous increase of 70%  in its median house price since 2010

 + The trade area population for Truganina Central is forecast to increase at a rate of 17% per annum to 2031**

For further information please contact:

Rorey James

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: INDUSTRIAL LAND - TWO LOTS 7,320SQM EACH & ADJOINING TITLES

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to exclusively bring to market 18 Apex Drive, Truganina within the highly sought after Crossing Estate.

Property highlights;
+ Block dimensions: 50.4m* x 105.2m* 
+ Block size: 5,302sqm*
+ Owner occupier or developer dream
+ Booming Precinct
+ Titled land
+ Industrial 3 Zone 
+ Nearby residential catchment
+ Only 22km* from Port of Melbourne, 24km* from Melbourne CBD and 27km* from Melbourne Airport 

The Crossing is an industrial 3 zoned estate, which boasts unrivalled proximity to the residential precinct of Truganina and Tarneit.

The current Western Road Upgrade Project will be completed in 2021. This will ensure that Palmers, Dohertys and Leakes Roads will improve efficiency of travel time for businesses operating in Melbourne’s West. Access to the city and freeway network via Leakes Road, and to the north via Palmers/Robinsons Road will be improved by this upgrade. Apex Drive will eventually provide a major thoroughfare/shortcut for vehicles driving from Palmers to Forsyth Road, increasing exposure to passing traffic for this site.

Wide roads, generous landscaping and zoning restrictions will ensure that this is a clean and desirable estate for decades to come. The Commercial 2 precincts on Leakes Road provide two important neighbouring offices, retail, food outlets and other retail amenity.

*approx.
